STYLING RULES: 
- Follow atomic design and reuse components from `/components`.
- Do not use inline styles.
- All buttons must use the <PrimaryButton> component with consistent layout.
- Position navigation buttons in a fixed bottom container.
- Use spacing scale from theme.
- Wrap every screen with <AppScreen> for padding and safe areas.
- Follow React Native accessibility best practices.
- Never hardcode colors or dimensions; use values from `theme.ts`.
- Always use Tailwind CSS.
- Always use Lucide icons.
